4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior experience, aiming to build expertise in cybersecurity. The program covers fundamental areas including Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. With a duration of 16 weeks, students participate in 3 live online classes weekly, within groups of up to 16 participants. Upon completion, students receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, which is recognized by various institutions. The course is available in English and Spanish, with no prior experience required. More information can be found at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop